  "composition_rules": [
    "A composition must declare one base architecture and zero or more specializations.",
    "Every specialization must bind each required input to a concrete parent output or remain blocked.",
    "Timing compatibility requires relative ticks and entity order, not only total repeater delay.",
    "Geometry compatibility requires chamber coordinates, direction axes, water corridors and collision envelopes.",
    "Payload compatibility must distinguish TNT-only, falling-block-required and archetype-selectable modes.",
    "A module cannot be promoted from static shape; runtime traces must establish its causal role.",
    "EC160 redistribution must preserve cohort sizes, facing ratios, symmetry, timing and output trajectory after every bank split.",
    "Live ExtremeCraft claims require a reduced canary before full-charge field use."
  ]
